OL,5, The smell hits you first - freshly     
OL,6, cooked rice, lentils and spinach,      
OL,7, served in ladles from steaming pots.   
OL,9,FDozens of families - including mothers 
OL,10,Fwith babies - are lined up with plates 
OL,11,Fto get a serving of what will likely be
OL,12,Ftheir only meal for the day.           
OL,14,F"We are here because we are hungry,"   
OL,15,Fsays Chandrika Manel, a mother of four.
OL,17,FAs she kneads a ball of rice with her  
OL,18,Fhands, mixing it with the lentils and  
OL,19,Fspinach before feeding it to one of her
OL,20,Fchildren, she explains that even buying
OL,21,Fbread is a struggle.                   
